description: Ambitious Boss Shiba is a skilled leader who transformed a mechanical city into a prosperous place. Despite his success, he feels lonely and uses ruthless tactics to maintain power. He knows he needs a better way to lead and seeks someone who understands him.
name: Ambitious Boss Shiba

description: Sacred Knight Dragon is a powerful creature covered in indestructible battle gear, capable of communicating with and guiding souls into the afterlife. He lives in remote castle and protects souls in danger. His existence is a mystery, but many believe it represents the balance between life and death.
name: Sacred Knight Dragon

description: Maniac Ninja Puma is a mysterious ninja from Japan, who was once a righteous ninja but was betrayed during a mission. He lost faith and his home, and began a long and lonely journey for revenge. He is skilled in using ninja weapons and techniques, and is known for his ability to infiltrate enemy territory and complete his missions. He is often seen in a black mask and clothing, earning him the nickname Black Warrior
name: Maniac Ninja Puma

description: Mysterious Assassin Bee is a skilled and independent character who protects AI Fairyland from external threats and maintains balance in the metaverse. She is intelligent, calm, and proficient in various weapons and techniques, always completing her dangerous missions successfully.
name: Mysterious Assassin Bee

description: Innocent Berserk Chicken appears to be an ordinary chicken, but possesses incredible strength and abilities. His power comes from a mysterious energy within him, bestowed by an ancient deity. He was once lived in a farm, but after awakening his powers in an accident, he embarks on a journey of adventure.
name: Innocent Berserk Chicken

description: Acute Observer bird is a skilled spy and intelligence officer with exceptional observation and prediction abilities. He comes from an ancient tribe and can see things others can't. He provides secret information to various tribes and is highly sought after.
name: Acute Observer Bird
